data.description: Welcome to this charming 1,896 square foot home located in Cleburne, TX. This lovely home boasts three spacious bedrooms and two well-appointed bathrooms. As you approach, you'll notice the extended driveway and convenient boat and trailer parking on the side of the home. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting atmosphere of he open and large living room. The laminate flooring adds a modern touch to the space while providing easy maintenance. The centerpiece of the living room is the lovely gas fireplace perfect for our upcoming chilly nights. The well designed eat-in kitchen features ample counter space and storage, making it ideal for cooking and entertaining. It is a great place to host your family for the holidays. The oversized covered patio is your personal backyard retreat. Enjoy family time or some alone time on this spacious back patio.
